_sText:
Medium sized fightyard map. 32 player spawn points. No buyzones. Works fine with Gungame.

Each round all players will automatically receive the same weapon. There are 15 different combinations, from knives only up to the auto-sniper. All players get HE and smoke grenades each round. Weapons are chosen at random so it is possible to receive the same weapon on two consecutive rounds.

Jernau's Maps site is at http://maps.playerofgames.net/
